Copycat- (6)
- Has the ability to visit someone, and watch them. If they survive that night, they will learn the role of the person they visited, and gain their powers for 1 night.
- The copycat can use the power they learnt for that night, or choose to visit someone else. If they watched no one last night or if they have no abilites to use, the copycat can only visit someone.
- Copying someone is a night end action, and is a visiting action. Has no cooldown.
- Respawns in 6 phases.
